summary: This document appears to be a law enforcement lieutenant's log and daily activity report for August 4, 2019, from the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) in New York. It is likely related to the monitoring of Jeffrey Epstein while he was in custody, given the date is shortly before his death.

events.title: Daily Correctional Center Log
events.description: A lieutenant's log and daily activity report was generated for the Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York.

keyFacts: The document is a law enforcement log dated August 4, 2019, from the Metropolitan Correctional Center.
Jeffrey Epstein was in custody at the MCC in August 2019 and died on August 10, 2019.
The log is marked as CONFIDENTIAL and is part of the SDNY (Southern District of New York) case files.
